data.description: Charming Family Appeal With Endless Possibilities! This 3 bedrooms, 2 bath home sits on .19 acres in Jerome, ID. It is boasting 2,688 sqft with room for improvements. It sits in a prime location with a ton of upgrades. New roof, new siding, new HVAC system, along with so much more. The beautiful yard has lush landscaping and trees with an oversized back yard with ally access. The interior is roomy with a lot of potential. The main level has 3 bedrooms and 1 bath. The below grade has 1 bath with an open floorpan for storage or the ability to add a second living space. This home is priced to move and won't last long. Come see it today!
